<div class="goods-col_img">
<img src="https://img.furusato-tax.jp/img/x/product/details/20221110/pd_049e9093a305dac49dfed9484e062febeae37fc5.jpg" alt="サンプル写真" class="goods-col_photo" decoding="async" />
